# ============================================================================
# Cloudflare Pages / Netlify _headers file — security headers for the static site.
#
# IMPORTANT: GitHub Pages does NOT honor this file. It is only effective when
# the site is hosted on Cloudflare Pages or Netlify (or another host that reads
# `_headers`). If you keep using GitHub Pages, deploy these headers via a
# Cloudflare Page Rule or Transform Rule on the `fuluckpet.com` zone instead.
#
# When you migrate to Cloudflare Pages:
#   1. Connect this repo as a Pages project.
#   2. Pages will read this file automatically — no extra config needed.
#   3. Verify with `curl -I https://fuluckpet.com/` that the headers are set.
#
# CSP allowlist notes:
#   - `script-src` allows GA4 + TikTok + Instagram + YouTube embeds (already in use).
#   - `connect-src` allows the Workers API and GA. Add other origins if you
#     introduce new third-party fetches.
#   - `img-src https:` is wide on purpose — many embeds load images from
#     arbitrary CDNs. Tighten only if you can enumerate every image origin.
#   - 'unsafe-inline' for script-src is required because i18n.js sets dataset
#     fields inline; consider hashed CSP later.
# ============================================================================

/*
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=63072000; includeSubDomains; preload
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  X-Frame-Options: SAMEORIGIN
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: camera=(), microphone=(), geolocation=()
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'; script-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://www.googletagmanager.com https://*.google-analytics.com https://www.tiktok.com https://platform.instagram.com https://www.youtube.com; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://fonts.googleapis.com; font-src 'self' https://fonts.gstatic.com; img-src 'self' data: https: blob:; connect-src 'self' https://fuluck-api.mouxue56.workers.dev https://*.google-analytics.com; frame-src https://www.youtube.com https://www.tiktok.com https://platform.instagram.com; frame-ancestors 'self';
